00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:58.950 line:80%
Come on, go back to the bridal chamber.

00:01:58.950 --> 00:01:59.670 line:80%
Go on now.

00:02:10.230 --> 00:02:10.880 line:80%
Wait.

00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:15.200 line:80%
