00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:10.240 line:80%
The day Song Yan came looking for trouble,
didn't we already k...

00:03:13.990 --> 00:03:15.320 line:80%
Didn't we already kiss?

00:03:17.510 --> 00:03:19.950 line:80%
