00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:25.200 line:80%
Then when I carried you back
from the snow that day—

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:27.000 line:80%
that counts as intimacy, right?

00:03:29.780 --> 00:03:30.430 line:80%
Yeah, that counts.

00:03:30.430 --> 00:03:35.900 line:80%
[Happiness]

00:03:31.150 --> 00:03:32.350 line:80%
Then that settles it.

00:03:37.990 --> 00:03:38.830 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:03:39.480 --> 00:03:41.230 line:80%
I don't have any improper intentions
toward you.

00:03:41.230 --> 00:03:42.430 line:80%
With all your injuries,

00:03:41.270 --> 00:03:43.460 line:80%
[Happiness]

00:03:42.879 --> 00:03:45.340 line:80%
