it'd be useless.

00:03:51.990 --> 00:03:53.160 line:80%
Fan Changyu.

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:55.820 line:80%
Listen to the nonsense you're spouting.

00:04:00.770 --> 00:04:03.360 line:80%
With this kind of medicine,
you don't need to...

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:05.160 line:80%
You don't need to apply too much.

00:04:06.200 --> 00:04:07.000 line:80%
Is it too much?

00:04:08.710 --> 00:04:10.920 line:80%
But I saw Mr. Zhao use this much.

00:04:15.160 --> 00:04:16.230 line:80%
You changed the medicine?

00:04:16.230 --> 00:04:17.490 line:80%
How come I didn't know?

00:04:18.190 --> 00:04:19.040 line:80%
It's fine.

00:04:19.750 --> 00:04:21.210 line:80%
Just help me bandage it up.

00:04:29.910 --> 00:04:30.980 line:80%
These wounds—

00:04:31.760 --> 00:04:33.959 line:80%
