00:04:35.430 --> 00:04:38.560 line:80%
I didn't even notice
when I changed your clothes before.

00:04:38.830 --> 00:04:39.670 line:80%
It's nothing.

00:04:40.990 --> 00:04:45.590 line:80%
I didn't want you to come exactly because
I was worried my injuries would scare you.

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:48.670 line:80%
Bear with it.

00:04:48.670 --> 00:04:50.530 line:80%
I'll have it bandaged in a second.

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:17.570 line:80%
Others rely on their skills
to escort valuables,

00:05:17.960 --> 00:05:20.040 line:80%
but you rely on sheer luck.

00:05:24.670 --> 00:05:26.670 line:80%
Don't take such risks in the future.

00:05:26.870 --> 00:05:27.800 line:80%
If it comes to it,

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:29.920 line:80%
I'll just work harder

00:05:31.180 --> 00:05:34.040 line:80%
