to provide for you.

00:05:53.670 --> 00:05:56.200 line:80%
I'll go down
and sleep with Changning in a bit.

00:05:56.570 --> 00:05:57.400 line:80%
No need.

00:05:57.840 --> 00:05:58.630 line:80%
In a bit,

00:05:59.920 --> 00:06:02.250 line:80%
I'll go sleep in the main room downstairs.

00:06:03.430 --> 00:06:04.290 line:80%
That works too.

00:06:05.870 --> 00:06:07.280 line:80%
I'll fetch you a basin of water.

00:06:07.280 --> 00:06:08.810 line:80%
You can wipe yourself down.

00:06:13.510 --> 00:06:15.100 line:80%
I'll take the wedding robes down for you.

00:06:14.590 --> 00:06:15.540 line:80%
[Intimacy Instruction Drawings]

00:06:18.460 --> 00:06:19.380 line:80%
[Intimacy Instruction Drawings]

00:06:37.110 --> 00:06:39.310 line:80%
