00:06:48.959 --> 00:06:50.670 line:80%
I won't hold it against you this time.

00:06:50.670 --> 00:06:52.160 line:80%
I'll throw this filthy thing away for you.

00:06:52.160 --> 00:06:53.360 line:80%
No more reading this!

00:07:00.840 --> 00:07:01.870 line:80%
So embarrassing.

00:07:08.840 --> 00:07:09.670 line:80%
What is it?

00:07:11.690 --> 00:07:12.920 line:80%
Come back, come back.

00:07:13.630 --> 00:07:15.570 line:80%
Careful, don't get caught.

00:07:22.310 --> 00:07:23.600 line:80%
She's coming down.

00:07:56.840 --> 00:07:57.480 line:80%
Look.

00:07:57.900 --> 00:07:59.070 line:80%
Was I right or not?

00:07:59.220 --> 00:08:02.550 line:80%
They're sleeping in separate rooms
on their wedding night.

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:05.190 line:80%
Their marriage must be fake.

00:08:05.850 --> 00:08:06.760 line:80%
Darling,

00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:08.430 line:80%
you really are amazing.

00:08:08.670 --> 00:08:10.070 line:80%
That wretched girl

00:08:10.190 --> 00:08:12.310 line:80%
