00:08:28.870 --> 00:08:30.310 line:80%
Go over there and look.

00:08:42.780 --> 00:08:44.680 line:80%
Darling, this can't be right.

00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:47.000 line:80%
She fetched a basin of water
and went back to the room.

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:48.550 line:80%
