00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:33.410 line:80%
Go close the window.

00:09:34.760 --> 00:09:35.360 line:80%
Okay.

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:45.190 line:80%
What's this supposed to mean?

00:09:45.190 --> 00:09:46.790 line:80%
They even closed the window.

00:09:47.070 --> 00:09:48.400 line:80%
That's impossible.

00:09:48.710 --> 00:09:50.250 line:80%
In such a short time,

00:09:50.830 --> 00:09:52.590 line:80%
