deal with her?

00:09:54.420 --> 00:09:55.680 line:80%
Something must be off.

00:10:04.670 --> 00:10:05.800 line:80%
Give me the candles.

00:10:13.350 --> 00:10:14.150 line:80%
Sit over here.

00:10:31.640 --> 00:10:32.430 line:80%
Turn around.

00:10:41.280 --> 00:10:42.310 line:80%
Come closer.

00:10:51.430 --> 00:10:53.280 line:80%
A-Are they about to
consummate the marriage?

00:10:53.280 --> 00:10:55.050 line:80%
Right here in the main room...

00:10:55.240 --> 00:10:56.840 line:80%
Consummating the marriage?

00:11:00.860 --> 00:11:03.870 line:80%
Your clothes are soaked with sweat.

00:11:04.100 --> 00:11:05.300 line:80%
