00:13:55.120 --> 00:13:56.100 line:80%
It's not a cat?

00:13:56.400 --> 00:13:57.470 line:80%
Who's out there?

00:14:04.550 --> 00:14:06.140 line:80%
As expected from a beast.

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:07.350 line:80%
Shameless thing.

00:14:07.370 --> 00:14:08.900 line:80%
Stealing meat in the middle of the night.

00:14:08.900 --> 00:14:10.160 line:80%
If I catch you next time,

00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:11.490 line:80%
