00:14:15.990 --> 00:14:19.720 line:80%
Could that wretched girl
really have consummated their marriage?

00:14:20.760 --> 00:14:22.590 line:80%
Then... Then let's hurry
and get out of here.

00:14:22.590 --> 00:14:25.000 line:80%
Or we'll end up kicking the bucket
right here.

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.000 line:80%
Hurry up. Come on.

00:14:57.710 --> 00:14:58.440 line:80%
Thanks a lot.

00:15:24.280 --> 00:15:26.140 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:15:39.920 --> 00:15:40.880 line:80%
Just this piece, right?

00:15:40.880 --> 00:15:41.880 line:80%
Yeah, this piece.

