00:16:24.470 --> 00:16:25.470 line:80%
Mrs. Yin.

00:16:25.950 --> 00:16:26.640 line:80%
Changyu,

00:16:27.200 --> 00:16:29.200 line:80%
why open up right after the wedding?

00:16:29.240 --> 00:16:30.650 line:80%
