00:16:32.640 --> 00:16:34.850 line:80%
to get my parents' pig shed
running again soon,

00:16:34.850 --> 00:16:36.050 line:80%
so I have to work hard.

00:16:37.320 --> 00:16:40.200 line:80%
True, another mouth to feed at home.

00:16:40.350 --> 00:16:41.680 line:80%
You do need to work hard.

00:16:43.880 --> 00:16:45.400 line:80%
That matrilocal husband of yours—

00:16:45.400 --> 00:16:47.310 line:80%
