00:18:18.150 --> 00:18:20.610 line:80%
[Luo's Pawnshop]

00:18:27.860 --> 00:18:28.920 line:80%
[One silver hairpin pawned for
2 taels of pure silver]

00:18:27.960 --> 00:18:29.070 line:80%
It's sold. Sold already.

00:18:29.070 --> 00:18:29.960 line:80%
Sold?

00:18:30.960 --> 00:18:32.340 line:80%
How could you sell it?

00:18:32.830 --> 00:18:34.230 line:80%
It was a redeemable pawn.

00:18:34.280 --> 00:18:36.080 line:80%
Look closely at the pawn ticket.

00:18:36.630 --> 00:18:38.310 line:80%
It was indeed a redeemable pawn,

00:18:38.310 --> 00:18:40.480 line:80%
but there's a stipulation:

00:18:40.620 --> 00:18:45.030 line:80%
[Luo's Pawnshop]

00:18:40.910 --> 00:18:43.480 line:80%
