the contract.

00:19:03.870 --> 00:19:05.200 line:80%
I really don't understand.

00:19:05.200 --> 00:19:06.370 line:80%
Just a crude silver hairpin—

00:19:06.370 --> 00:19:07.680 line:80%
that gentleman wanted it,

00:19:07.680 --> 00:19:08.780 line:80%
