rare or valuable.

00:19:09.870 --> 00:19:10.800 line:80%
What gentleman?

00:19:10.830 --> 00:19:11.690 line:80%
Where did he go?

00:19:12.480 --> 00:19:14.040 line:80%
Well, the customer's information...

00:19:14.040 --> 00:19:14.680 line:80%
Speak!

00:19:20.870 --> 00:19:22.270 line:80%
That was the only memento

00:19:22.800 --> 00:19:24.330 line:80%
