00:21:01.310 --> 00:21:03.510 line:80%
Didn't I come up with a solution for you?

00:21:07.710 --> 00:21:08.990 line:80%
Look at this.

00:21:10.390 --> 00:21:12.190 line:80%
Now the ants can't eat it, right?

00:21:12.520 --> 00:21:14.110 line:80%
You are amazing, Dad.

00:21:14.200 --> 00:21:14.960 line:80%
Can you

00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:17.510 line:80%
hide these candies in there for me?

00:21:19.270 --> 00:21:20.490 line:80%
You little rascal.

00:21:20.720 --> 00:21:22.790 line:80%
I knew you were hiding more candy.

00:21:23.040 --> 00:21:24.720 line:80%
Don't tell your mother.

00:21:24.740 --> 00:21:26.520 line:80%
Or she'll scold both of us.

00:21:26.520 --> 00:21:27.820 line:80%
Got it, Dad.

00:21:29.910 --> 00:21:31.760 line:80%
Go pick a blade of grass for me.

00:21:35.550 --> 00:21:36.480 line:80%
Here, Dad.

00:21:39.870 --> 00:21:41.000 line:80%
This way,

00:21:41.830 --> 00:21:43.240 line:80%
you won't lose it, right?

00:21:43.550 --> 00:21:44.980 line:80%
You're the best, Dad.

00:21:45.350 --> 00:21:46.130 line:80%
You, oh you.

00:21:49.480 --> 00:21:50.150 line:80%
Remember:

00:21:50.590 --> 00:21:52.350 line:80%
hardships come, hardships go.

00:21:52.960 --> 00:21:53.960 line:80%
Tears may fall,

00:21:54.110 --> 00:21:55.800 line:80%
but you must keep moving forward.

00:21:55.800 --> 00:21:58.110 line:80%
Even if the sky falls, there's always
someone taller to hold it up.

00:21:58.110 --> 00:22:00.730 line:80%
We must always eat well and sleep well.

00:22:00.760 --> 00:22:01.960 line:80%
Got it, Dad.

00:22:02.590 --> 00:22:03.360 line:80%
Good girl.

00:22:32.110 --> 00:22:33.520 line:80%
Thank you.

00:22:33.820 --> 00:22:35.340 line:80%
Many thanks.

00:22:35.520 --> 00:22:36.630 line:80%
See you another day.

00:22:36.630 --> 00:22:37.480 line:80%
See you.

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:38.350 line:80%
I'm off.

00:22:40.070 --> 00:22:41.440 line:80%
Take care.

00:22:41.480 --> 00:22:42.800 line:80%
Ms. Song.

00:22:43.680 --> 00:22:44.760 line:80%
Ms. Song.

00:22:44.830 --> 00:22:47.480 line:80%
You're moving to a big mansion
in the city, right?

00:22:47.480 --> 00:22:49.410 line:80%
How blessed you are.

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:51.350 line:80%
The County Magistrate
thinks highly of him,

00:22:51.350 --> 00:22:53.610 line:80%
and our Yan has lived up to expectations.

00:22:53.630 --> 00:22:54.870 line:80%
I'm thinking next year,

00:22:54.870 --> 00:22:56.110 line:80%
he'll take first place in
all 3 imperial exams

00:22:56.110 --> 00:22:58.280 line:80%
and bring glory to our town.

00:22:58.300 --> 00:22:59.960 line:80%
He'll surely pass with flying colors.

00:22:59.960 --> 00:23:02.200 line:80%
I'll take your good word for it, Sis.

00:23:05.070 --> 00:23:06.110 line:80%
Sis,

00:23:06.350 --> 00:23:09.800 line:80%
now that your Song Yan is about to become

00:23:09.800 --> 00:23:12.280 line:80%
the County Magistrate's son-in-law,

00:23:13.310 --> 00:23:16.960 line:80%
as for your promise of getting
my eldest grandson out of corvée labor

00:23:16.960 --> 00:23:19.630 line:80%
and finding him a job
as a police runner back home—

00:23:19.630 --> 00:23:21.280 line:80%
when will that happen?

00:23:24.150 --> 00:23:27.580 line:80%
I've spread the word to the whole village

00:23:27.680 --> 00:23:30.040 line:80%
that Fan Changyu is a jinx for you.

00:23:30.480 --> 00:23:31.280 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:23:31.590 --> 00:23:33.850 line:80%
When did I ever ask you
to spread any word?

00:23:34.730 --> 00:23:36.610 line:80%
No, no. Nothing.

00:23:36.640 --> 00:23:37.900 line:80%
I didn't say anything.

00:23:38.350 --> 00:23:39.610 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:23:40.070 --> 00:23:41.440 line:80%
When there's a chance,

00:23:41.480 --> 00:23:44.010 line:80%
I'll have Yan speak to
the County Magistrate.

00:23:44.040 --> 00:23:45.500 line:80%
Understood. Understood.

00:23:46.310 --> 00:23:47.970 line:80%
Fan Changyu, hold on, please.

00:23:49.520 --> 00:23:50.760 line:80%
Stop right there!

00:23:52.550 --> 00:23:54.510 line:80%
Hardships come, hardships go.

00:23:54.960 --> 00:23:58.620 line:80%
Even if the sky falls, there's always
someone taller to hold it up.

00:24:04.390 --> 00:24:07.850 line:80%
We've been neighbors for years,
and we may not meet ever again.

00:24:08.360 --> 00:24:10.360 line:80%
This is a token of our appreciation.

00:24:10.390 --> 00:24:11.590 line:80%
Please accept it.

00:24:12.040 --> 00:24:14.870 line:80%
And please, return
the betrothal letter to us.

00:24:15.910 --> 00:24:16.800 line:80%
Exactly.

00:24:17.040 --> 00:24:19.070 line:80%
Now that you've taken a matrilocal husband
and gotten married,

00:24:19.070 --> 00:24:21.070 line:80%
why keep their betrothal letter?

00:24:25.520 --> 00:24:26.520 line:80%
That's all?

00:24:27.820 --> 00:24:30.160 line:80%
How much do we owe you exactly?

00:24:30.520 --> 00:24:32.870 line:80%
Besides, when did that even happen?

00:24:32.900 --> 00:24:34.040 line:80%
And who saw it?

00:24:34.830 --> 00:24:35.590 line:80%
Exactly.

00:24:35.780 --> 00:24:37.840 line:80%
Without proof, who would believe it?

00:24:38.000 --> 00:24:40.240 line:80%
If the Song family really
borrowed money from you,

00:24:40.240 --> 00:24:42.680 line:80%
you would have asked for it back
the next year.

00:24:42.680 --> 00:24:45.280 line:80%
Who would give charity for over a decade

00:24:45.280 --> 00:24:47.150 line:80%
without expecting anything in return?
Right?

00:24:47.150 --> 00:24:49.880 line:80%
That would make them a living saint,
wouldn't it?

00:24:57.240 --> 00:24:58.240 line:80%
Fine, never mind.

00:24:59.720 --> 00:25:01.400 line:80%
I'll give you all this money.

00:25:01.590 --> 00:25:02.480 line:80%
This must be enough, right?

00:25:02.480 --> 00:25:04.410 line:80%
Give us back the betrothal letter.

00:25:10.450 --> 00:25:11.930 line:80%
Everyone, look!

00:25:12.310 --> 00:25:14.240 line:80%
Even this much money isn't enough.

00:25:14.350 --> 00:25:15.960 line:80%
You, Fan Changyu,

00:25:15.960 --> 00:25:17.630 line:80%
are truly insatiable!

00:25:18.280 --> 00:25:19.940 line:80%
You've been blinded by greed!

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:21.480 line:80%
What kind of person is she?

00:25:23.630 --> 00:25:25.750 line:80%
Move. Move aside.

00:25:25.830 --> 00:25:27.480 line:80%
Bad people are bullying Changyu,

00:25:27.480 --> 00:25:29.480 line:80%
and Zheng is here to back her up.

00:25:35.720 --> 00:25:36.480 line:80%
Who is this?

00:25:36.900 --> 00:25:38.510 line:80%
This is Changyu's husband.

00:25:38.590 --> 00:25:39.590 line:80%
Him?

00:25:39.870 --> 00:25:41.100 line:80%
And he's a cripple.

00:25:43.910 --> 00:25:45.300 line:80%
Your wounds haven't healed.

00:25:45.300 --> 00:25:46.340 line:80%
It's hard for you to move around.

00:25:46.340 --> 00:25:48.340 line:80%
Why are you messing around with her?

00:25:48.460 --> 00:25:49.220 line:80%
It's fine.

00:25:52.280 --> 00:25:54.140 line:80%
Even if my wounds haven't healed,

00:25:54.630 --> 00:25:57.230 line:80%
it doesn't stop me from
coming to take you home.

00:26:00.280 --> 00:26:04.000 line:80%
What does the Fan family's business have
to do with a matrilocal husband like you?

00:26:04.000 --> 00:26:05.460 line:80%
My surname is also Fan now.

00:26:06.520 --> 00:26:07.680 line:80%
You want an IOU?

00:26:08.120 --> 00:26:08.750 line:80%
Fine.

00:26:09.630 --> 00:26:12.490 line:80%
Clear the debts you Song family
owes the Fan family,

00:26:12.630 --> 00:26:13.800 line:80%
then you can move.

00:26:15.390 --> 00:26:17.630 line:80%
One coffin—6 taels and 20 mace.

00:26:18.130 --> 00:26:20.530 line:80%
Twelve chi of fine cloth—
1 tael and 10 mace.

00:26:21.310 --> 00:26:23.640 line:80%
Thirty baskets of eggs—
1 tael and 50 mace.

00:26:24.960 --> 00:26:27.720 line:80%
Three years of tuition—
9 taels and 60 mace.

00:26:29.480 --> 00:26:31.350 line:80%
Song Yan, that poor scholar,

00:26:31.720 --> 00:26:33.500 line:80%
only managed to study thanks to

00:26:33.530 --> 00:26:35.260 line:80%
the Fan family supporting him.

00:26:35.280 --> 00:26:36.280 line:80%
Who would have thought that

00:26:36.280 --> 00:26:38.910 line:80%
as soon as Song Yan became
a provincial candidate,

00:26:38.910 --> 00:26:41.180 line:80%
while Fan Erniu and his wife
were barely cold in their graves,

00:26:41.180 --> 00:26:43.780 line:80%
he forced Changyu to
break off the engagement?

00:26:43.910 --> 00:26:45.390 line:80%
Song's mother's living expenses

00:26:45.390 --> 00:26:47.240 line:80%
were also paid for
entirely by Changyu's family.

00:26:47.240 --> 00:26:48.040 line:80%
How shameless.

00:26:48.040 --> 00:26:48.910 line:80%
Exactly.

00:26:53.440 --> 00:26:55.770 line:80%
Mr. Zhao, what exactly were the expenses?

00:26:55.800 --> 00:26:58.690 line:80%
They paid 3 years of tuition
for that ingrate.

00:26:58.910 --> 00:27:01.520 line:80%
One year alone costs 3 taels and 20 mace.

00:27:01.920 --> 00:27:04.580 line:80%
Do the math—how much would that be
after 3 years?

00:27:04.800 --> 00:27:06.070 line:80%
Nine taels and 60 mace.

00:27:06.550 --> 00:27:07.680 line:80%
That's quite a lot.

00:27:07.700 --> 00:27:09.910 line:80%
And the pork they begged for
during festivals—

00:27:09.910 --> 00:27:11.800 line:80%
at least 20 pieces.

00:27:11.960 --> 00:27:13.910 line:80%
That must add up to
over 2 taels of silver.

00:27:13.910 --> 00:27:16.510 line:80%
And when Song Yan got sick
the year before last,

00:27:16.520 --> 00:27:18.750 line:80%
the medicine alone cost over a tael.

00:27:18.830 --> 00:27:20.360 line:80%
Fan Erniu paid for that too.

00:27:20.490 --> 00:27:21.690 line:80%
He didn't even dare tell his wife

00:27:21.690 --> 00:27:23.150 line:80%
or Changyu.

00:27:23.150 --> 00:27:24.680 line:80%
The more we talk about it,
the madder I get.

00:27:24.680 --> 00:27:26.410 line:80%
Even the women's items like...

00:27:32.000 --> 00:27:34.730 line:80%
And 4 packs of bamboo baskets,
30 bundles of wood,

00:27:34.760 --> 00:27:35.550 line:80%
5 buckets of lamp oil,

00:27:35.550 --> 00:27:36.550 line:80%
3 copper basins,

00:27:37.330 --> 00:27:38.420 line:80%
one bamboo mat,

00:27:38.440 --> 00:27:39.460 line:80%
and...

00:27:40.440 --> 00:27:41.160 line:80%
Changning, come back.

00:27:41.160 --> 00:27:42.620 line:80%
Don't fall into the ditch.

00:27:44.440 --> 00:27:47.000 line:80%
And 4 bundles of menstrual cloths.

00:27:48.590 --> 00:27:49.440 line:80%
Menstrual cloths?

00:27:49.440 --> 00:27:52.520 line:80%
-They even borrowed the menstrual cloths?
-And last year on the Dragon Boat Festival,

00:27:52.520 --> 00:27:54.070 line:80%
Mrs. Song came to visit

00:27:54.200 --> 00:27:57.390 line:80%
and took the chance to steal
a braised pig's tail.

00:27:59.170 --> 00:28:00.650 line:80%
So, all things considered,

00:28:00.650 --> 00:28:01.700 line:80%
the Fan family

00:28:01.720 --> 00:28:04.380 line:80%
basically provided for
the Song mother and son.

00:28:04.810 --> 00:28:07.350 line:80%
Granny Kang, you were speaking up
for the Song family just now—

00:28:07.350 --> 00:28:09.550 line:80%
how much of the benefits did you pocket?

00:28:09.720 --> 00:28:11.030 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense.

00:28:11.070 --> 00:28:12.750 line:80%
I've never gotten anything out of it.

00:28:12.750 --> 00:28:14.310 line:80%
I'm just like everyone else.

00:28:14.310 --> 00:28:15.990 line:80%
I was just passing by.

00:28:16.150 --> 00:28:18.860 line:80%
Seriously, I've never gotten anything.

00:28:19.070 --> 00:28:20.650 line:80%
I was just passing by.

00:28:21.000 --> 00:28:22.390 line:80%
You're a grown man,

00:28:22.410 --> 00:28:25.070 line:80%
talking about women's filthy things
all the time—

00:28:25.070 --> 00:28:26.910 line:80%
what a disgrace to decency!

00:28:27.890 --> 00:28:30.800 line:80%
Menstruation is the foundation
of humanity and motherhood.

00:28:30.800 --> 00:28:32.590 line:80%
Why can't it be spoken of?

00:28:32.750 --> 00:28:34.830 line:80%
You say it can't be spoken of,

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:36.660 line:80%
but you sure ask for things often.

00:28:36.660 --> 00:28:38.820 line:80%
Exactly, asking for a whole bundle
at once.

00:28:38.820 --> 00:28:40.390 line:80%
If your period lasts half a month,

00:28:40.390 --> 00:28:42.280 line:80%
you'd better see a doctor soon.

00:28:42.280 --> 00:28:44.190 line:80%
-Go see a doctor.
-Go see a doctor.

00:28:44.520 --> 00:28:45.780 line:80%
None of your business!

00:28:46.200 --> 00:28:47.600 line:80%
What are you laughing at?

00:28:48.390 --> 00:28:49.800 line:80%
None of your business!

00:28:50.070 --> 00:28:51.070 line:80%
What's so funny?

00:28:51.150 --> 00:28:52.440 line:80%
It's none of your business!

00:28:52.440 --> 00:28:54.700 line:80%
Ladies, please don't use hurtful words.

00:28:56.150 --> 00:28:57.870 line:80%
You underestimate Mr. and Mrs. Fan's

00:28:57.870 --> 00:28:59.240 line:80%
sincere care for me.

00:28:59.870 --> 00:29:00.910 line:80%
They've passed away,

00:29:00.910 --> 00:29:02.770 line:80%
so there should be no more gossip.

00:29:03.110 --> 00:29:03.680 line:80%
Changyu.

00:29:04.990 --> 00:29:07.250 line:80%
Although you always speak harshly to me,

00:29:07.680 --> 00:29:08.760 line:80%
I don't blame you.

00:29:10.440 --> 00:29:12.630 line:80%
I know your hasty marriage this time

00:29:13.240 --> 00:29:14.770 line:80%
has something to do with me.

00:29:16.480 --> 00:29:17.810 line:80%
Even though from now on,

00:29:17.910 --> 00:29:19.480 line:80%
we'll go our separate ways,

00:29:20.480 --> 00:29:22.680 line:80%
if you encounter trouble in the future,

00:29:22.800 --> 00:29:25.400 line:80%
just send someone to my mansion
and let me know.

00:29:25.440 --> 00:29:27.110 line:80%
I will always be your Brother Song Yan.

00:29:27.110 --> 00:29:27.960 line:80%
Bah!

00:29:28.630 --> 00:29:30.690 line:80%
Don't disgust me with that nonsense.

00:29:30.830 --> 00:29:32.310 line:80%
If not for my sake,

00:29:32.870 --> 00:29:35.930 line:80%
would my parents have treated
someone like you so well?

00:29:36.040 --> 00:29:38.040 line:80%
I blame myself for
being blind and foolish.

00:29:38.040 --> 00:29:39.070 line:80%
I was truly blind,

00:29:40.010 --> 00:29:42.510 line:80%
falling for a literate ingrate like you.

00:29:42.720 --> 00:29:43.120 line:80%
You...

00:29:43.390 --> 00:29:45.200 line:80%
You, pay up!

00:29:46.030 --> 00:29:46.870 line:80%
-That's right!
-Pay her!

00:29:46.870 --> 00:29:47.920 line:80%
-Pay her!
-Pay her!

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:48.750 line:80%
-Pay her!
-Pay her!

00:29:48.750 --> 00:29:49.960 line:80%
-Pay her!
-Pay her!

00:29:50.520 --> 00:29:51.310 line:80%
Fine.

00:29:52.390 --> 00:29:55.050 line:80%
A gentleman never speaks ill of
a former friend.

00:29:55.550 --> 00:29:56.790 line:80%
I will pay you back.

00:29:58.830 --> 00:29:59.910 line:80%
Removing the fraction,

00:29:59.910 --> 00:30:01.170 line:80%
it's 30 taels in total.

00:30:01.200 --> 00:30:03.860 line:80%
If you don't believe me,
calculate it yourself.

00:30:06.690 --> 00:30:07.330 line:80%
Mother,

00:30:08.090 --> 00:30:09.000 line:80%
pay her.

00:30:12.520 --> 00:30:14.380 line:80%
But we don't have that much money.

00:30:17.000 --> 00:30:18.350 line:80%
If you don't have enough money,

00:30:18.350 --> 00:30:19.480 line:80%
you can write an IOU.

00:30:21.110 --> 00:30:22.710 line:80%
There's no ink or brush here.

00:30:23.150 --> 00:30:24.820 line:80%
I'll write one and send it to you
once I move to the city.

00:30:24.820 --> 00:30:26.060 line:80%
Why do you need ink?

00:30:26.590 --> 00:30:28.070 line:80%
Bite your finger open,

00:30:28.480 --> 00:30:30.480 line:80%
and press your fingerprint. That will do.

00:30:30.480 --> 00:30:31.680 line:80%
Right. Press your fingerprint.

00:30:31.680 --> 00:30:33.500 line:80%
Just press your fingerprint.

00:30:33.630 --> 00:30:34.040 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:30:34.040 --> 00:30:35.180 line:80%
Absolutely not!

00:30:35.240 --> 00:30:36.440 line:80%
Don't listen to them.

00:30:37.350 --> 00:30:37.810 line:80%
This...

00:30:38.490 --> 00:30:39.750 line:80%
-Don't do that!
-Wait!

00:30:55.940 --> 00:30:57.590 line:80%
It's only a few dozen taels.

00:30:56.230 --> 00:30:59.270 line:80%
[Daughter of Magistrate Cui]

00:30:57.630 --> 00:30:58.960 line:80%
I'll pay it back for him.

00:31:02.910 --> 00:31:04.110 line:80%
Miss Cui Qianjin.

00:31:04.110 --> 00:31:07.190 line:80%
How could we trouble you
to step into such a lowly place?

00:31:08.350 --> 00:31:10.760 line:80%
Brother Song is my father's student.

00:31:11.070 --> 00:31:12.070 line:80%
It's only right

00:31:12.280 --> 00:31:13.340 line:80%
that I help him out.

00:31:14.910 --> 00:31:16.760 line:80%
How can a dignified imperial scholar

00:31:16.760 --> 00:31:18.650 line:80%
be schemed against and sullied

00:31:18.720 --> 00:31:20.520 line:80%
by some people reeking of money?

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:35.440 line:80%
Some are born with noble lives.

00:31:36.070 --> 00:31:36.760 line:80%
Like me.

00:31:37.630 --> 00:31:39.830 line:80%
My father named me Qianjin,

00:31:40.000 --> 00:31:42.150 line:80%
destining me to never lack gold or silver,

00:31:42.150 --> 00:31:43.680 line:80%
and to order others around.

00:31:44.390 --> 00:31:47.480 line:80%
Some are born with cheap lives.

00:31:48.110 --> 00:31:48.800 line:80%
Like you.

00:31:49.720 --> 00:31:51.390 line:80%
Both parents dead since childhood,

00:31:51.390 --> 00:31:53.240 line:80%
with no one to rely on in this life.

00:31:53.240 --> 00:31:54.910 line:80%
No matter how beautiful jade is,

00:31:54.910 --> 00:31:57.040 line:80%
it's not as valuable as gold or silver.

00:31:57.520 --> 00:31:58.720 line:80%
Here's 50 taels.

00:31:59.310 --> 00:32:00.370 line:80%
Go on and pick it up.

00:32:12.680 --> 00:32:13.810 line:80%
Stop it, Changning.

00:32:14.200 --> 00:32:15.860 line:80%
We won't take what's not ours.

00:32:16.390 --> 00:32:18.550 line:80%
The betrothal letter has long been placed
under the stone slab

00:32:18.550 --> 00:32:20.010 line:80%
at your house's doorstep.

00:32:20.720 --> 00:32:21.350 line:80%
Mother...

00:32:22.590 --> 00:32:24.720 line:80%
Things have long been over between us.

00:32:25.550 --> 00:32:27.950 line:80%
Consider the extra money as interest.

00:32:28.110 --> 00:32:30.070 line:80%
After all, your dignity

00:32:30.550 --> 00:32:31.950 line:80%
isn't worth much anyway.

00:32:32.230 --> 00:32:33.910 line:80%
I won't take a penny less than
what I'm owed,

00:32:33.910 --> 00:32:35.390 line:80%
and I won't take a penny
that isn't supposed to be mine.

00:32:35.390 --> 00:32:36.070 line:80%
Besides,

00:32:37.510 --> 00:32:38.910 line:80%
he's not worth anything.

00:32:41.680 --> 00:32:43.680 line:80%
Wait! I haven't finished speaking!

00:32:43.730 --> 00:32:44.530 line:80%
Get back here!

00:32:44.550 --> 00:32:45.310 line:80%
-How rude!
-Yan.

00:32:45.310 --> 00:32:46.870 line:80%
Yan, come and help!

00:32:47.110 --> 00:32:47.680 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:32:49.630 --> 00:32:50.520 line:80%
Whoever goes to help,

00:32:50.520 --> 00:32:52.450 line:80%
the silver on the ground is theirs!

00:33:06.450 --> 00:33:07.980 line:80%
Alright, alright. Come on.

00:33:10.240 --> 00:33:11.000 line:80%
Finally...

00:33:14.800 --> 00:33:15.960 line:80%
Finally found it.

00:33:17.800 --> 00:33:18.780 line:80%
Tear it up.

00:33:23.770 --> 00:33:25.700 line:80%
Changning, go home with Zheng.

00:33:47.910 --> 00:33:49.840 line:80%
He's just a provincial candidate.

00:33:50.000 --> 00:33:51.920 line:80%
In our Great Yin's 1 capital city
and 17 prefectures,

00:33:51.920 --> 00:33:53.720 line:80%
how many provincial candidates
are there each year?

00:33:53.720 --> 00:33:55.650 line:80%
What does a mere Song Yan count for?

00:33:59.390 --> 00:34:00.650 line:80%
You can say such things

00:34:00.830 --> 00:34:02.480 line:80%
in front of me,

00:34:03.180 --> 00:34:05.240 line:80%
but don't say them in front of outsiders.

00:34:05.240 --> 00:34:06.440 line:80%
You'll be laughed at.

00:34:06.520 --> 00:34:07.440 line:80%
Laughed at?

00:34:08.910 --> 00:34:09.830 line:80%
For what?

00:34:10.430 --> 00:34:11.789 line:80%
They'll laugh at you

00:34:11.870 --> 00:34:14.269 line:80%
for not even being a provincial candidate.

00:34:19.030 --> 00:34:21.720 line:80%
I know you're just saying this
to cheer me up.

00:34:23.820 --> 00:34:25.120 line:80%
Why would I try to cheer you up?

00:34:25.120 --> 00:34:26.600 line:80%
Don't mention a provincial candidate—

00:34:26.600 --> 00:34:27.999 line:80%
even an imperial scholar

00:34:28.390 --> 00:34:29.680 line:80%
is nothing special.

00:34:32.640 --> 00:34:35.990 line:80%
Do you really think of yourself
as a high-ranking official or something?

00:34:35.990 --> 00:34:36.280 line:80%
I...

00:34:36.470 --> 00:34:37.820 line:80%
I think you're smart,

00:34:38.280 --> 00:34:40.200 line:80%
and your handwriting is nice, too.

00:34:40.200 --> 00:34:42.990 line:80%
Why don't you go study
and take the imperial exams too?

00:34:42.990 --> 00:34:44.430 line:80%
If you happen to pass
and become a provincial candidate,

00:34:44.430 --> 00:34:46.510 line:80%
you might also land yourself
an official position.

00:34:46.510 --> 00:34:48.439 line:80%
I have no interest in officialdom.

00:34:51.280 --> 00:34:52.830 line:80%
That's a shame.

00:34:53.039 --> 00:34:56.030 line:80%
I was hoping you'd become
a very, very, very high-ranking official—

00:34:56.030 --> 00:34:59.560 line:80%
so you could find some reason
to make life hard for that Song guy.

00:35:01.690 --> 00:35:02.240 line:80%
Okay.

00:35:07.510 --> 00:35:08.310 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:35:12.510 --> 00:35:13.910 line:80%
Actually, I'm not sad

00:35:15.310 --> 00:35:16.470 line:80%
because of Song Yan.

00:35:18.600 --> 00:35:21.730 line:80%
I'm sad because I couldn't get
my mother's hairpin back.

00:35:33.240 --> 00:35:36.700 line:80%
-Actually, that hairpin...
-I've really let my parents down.

00:35:37.160 --> 00:35:39.390 line:80%
I clearly pawned it as a redeemable pawn,

00:35:39.390 --> 00:35:41.430 line:80%
but I happened to run into
a dishonest shopkeeper

00:35:41.430 --> 00:35:43.870 line:80%
who sold it to
some dim-witted young gentleman.

00:35:43.870 --> 00:35:45.090 line:80%
That darn gentleman

00:35:45.120 --> 00:35:46.720 line:80%
actually paid 20 taels of silver for it!

00:35:46.720 --> 00:35:48.320 line:80%
20 taels of silver, you know?

00:35:48.390 --> 00:35:49.980 line:80%
With that much money,

00:35:50.120 --> 00:35:52.120 line:80%
I could have made 3 hairpins for him.

00:35:53.210 --> 00:35:54.800 line:80%
How can there be such a person

00:35:54.800 --> 00:35:56.330 line:80%
who just causes trouble...

00:36:08.310 --> 00:36:09.790 line:80%
Why do you have this?

00:36:10.120 --> 00:36:11.180 line:80%
That gentleman...

00:36:15.310 --> 00:36:17.710 line:80%
So it was you who spent 20 taels
to redeem it?

00:36:19.680 --> 00:36:21.040 line:80%
Sort of.

00:36:25.940 --> 00:36:26.880 line:80%
It's back.

00:36:32.510 --> 00:36:33.200 line:80%
Wait.

00:36:33.910 --> 00:36:35.070 line:80%
So, all in all,

00:36:35.830 --> 00:36:38.720 line:80%
that dishonest shopkeeper
cheated you out of 20 taels?

00:36:38.720 --> 00:36:40.450 line:80%
I have to get that money back...

00:36:45.390 --> 00:36:46.870 line:80%
Actually, that gentleman

00:36:47.980 --> 00:36:49.590 line:80%
is the bookshop owner.

00:36:50.590 --> 00:36:52.660 line:80%
He bought this hairpin for 20 taels.

00:36:55.280 --> 00:36:56.830 line:80%
He appreciates my writings,

00:36:56.830 --> 00:36:59.910 line:80%
so when he sent someone
to deliver my payment,

00:37:00.200 --> 00:37:02.060 line:80%
he rewarded me with this hairpin.

00:37:02.240 --> 00:37:03.840 line:80%
That's quite a coincidence.

00:37:04.950 --> 00:37:05.560 line:80%
Yeah.

00:37:10.700 --> 00:37:11.700 line:80%
Here's the money.

00:37:17.390 --> 00:37:18.720 line:80%
You made that much money

00:37:19.110 --> 00:37:20.460 line:80%
selling essays?

00:37:20.650 --> 00:37:22.730 line:80%
Yes. Mr. Zhao can testify.

00:37:23.290 --> 00:37:24.620 line:80%
Where is that bookshop?

00:37:25.350 --> 00:37:26.830 line:80%
I'll go return the money
to that gentleman.

00:37:26.830 --> 00:37:27.430 line:80%
No need.

00:37:28.160 --> 00:37:29.960 line:80%
That gentleman is very wealthy.

00:37:30.120 --> 00:37:31.750 line:80%
He doesn't care about 20 taels.

00:37:31.750 --> 00:37:33.280 line:80%
I should at least thank him.

00:37:35.030 --> 00:37:35.950 line:80%
Of course.

00:37:37.030 --> 00:37:39.500 line:80%
When my injuries heal,

00:37:39.760 --> 00:37:41.220 line:80%
I'll take you to visit him.

00:37:42.720 --> 00:37:43.430 line:80%
Alright.

00:37:47.030 --> 00:37:47.950 line:80%
Actually,

00:37:48.510 --> 00:37:51.370 line:80%
you don't have to sell essays
to support the family.

00:37:52.720 --> 00:37:53.640 line:80%
I told you,

00:37:54.990 --> 00:37:57.050 line:80%
I can support you by butchering pigs.

00:38:19.780 --> 00:38:23.660 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:38:20.720 --> 00:38:21.470 line:80%
Mother.

00:38:21.830 --> 00:38:23.430 line:80%
I've retrieved the hairpin.

00:38:24.390 --> 00:38:25.160 line:80%
Before,

00:38:25.990 --> 00:38:28.590 line:80%
I kept worrying
that I'd done something wrong,

00:38:29.080 --> 00:38:30.720 line:80%
worried that you wouldn't approve of
what I did,

00:38:30.720 --> 00:38:32.320 line:80%
worried that you'd be angry.

00:38:33.310 --> 00:38:34.510 line:80%
Now that this hairpin

00:38:34.640 --> 00:38:36.170 line:80%
has found its way back to me,

00:38:37.760 --> 00:38:40.160 line:80%
it must be you watching over us
from beyond.

00:38:42.910 --> 00:38:45.240 line:80%
With that, my heart
can finally be at ease.

00:39:01.140 --> 00:39:02.000 line:80%
Let me help you.

00:40:12.540 --> 00:40:17.750 line:80%
[Luyuan Academy of Hejian]

00:40:44.560 --> 00:40:45.240 line:80%
An.

00:40:45.600 --> 00:40:46.280 line:80%
I've got drumsticks here.

00:40:46.280 --> 00:40:47.210 line:80%
Do you want some?

00:40:48.830 --> 00:40:49.430 line:80%
I...

00:40:51.200 --> 00:40:52.530 line:80%
I don't eat drumsticks.

00:40:52.550 --> 00:40:53.800 line:80%
I've got a big one here.

00:40:53.800 --> 00:40:54.830 line:80%
Look.

00:40:56.950 --> 00:40:58.510 line:80%
This is highly inappropriate.

00:40:58.510 --> 00:41:01.040 line:80%
How can you eat meat
in such a refined academy?

00:41:01.580 --> 00:41:04.440 line:80%
Aren't you worried
the Headmaster will punish you?

00:41:48.430 --> 00:41:49.620 line:80%
You stupid bird.

00:41:49.680 --> 00:41:51.740 line:80%
You get lost every time you come here.

00:41:56.870 --> 00:41:57.910 line:80%
I know, I know.

00:41:57.910 --> 00:41:59.710 line:80%
Wait a moment. Stay here for now.

00:42:02.160 --> 00:42:04.240 line:80%
Today's punishment copying
is considered done.

00:42:04.240 --> 00:42:05.160 line:80%
You may leave.

00:42:06.990 --> 00:42:08.280 line:80%
Thank you, Headmaster.

00:42:08.280 --> 00:42:10.200 line:80%
An, thank the Headmaster.

00:42:11.470 --> 00:42:13.270 line:80%
Thank you, Headmaster Gongsun.

00:42:20.320 --> 00:42:22.480 line:80%
I'm temporarily staying with the Fan family
in Lin'an Town to recover from my injuries.

00:42:22.200 --> 00:42:24.260 line:80%
[I'm temporarily staying with the Fan family
in Lin'an Town to recover from my injuries.]

00:42:23.280 --> 00:42:25.120 line:80%
I've brought my household registration
and travel permit with me

00:42:24.280 --> 00:42:25.890 line:80%
[I've brought my household registration
and travel permit with me for verification.]
[Jiuheng]

00:42:25.190 --> 00:42:26.250 line:80%
for verification.

00:42:34.030 --> 00:42:35.570 line:80%
Xie Jiuheng, you rascal.

00:42:35.870 --> 00:42:38.370 line:80%
I knew you wouldn't die so easily.